window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Most will die. Some will survive. A small few will thrive.</b></p> <p>The mysterious Overlords destroyed all electronics on Earth, imposed a game-like System, and unleashed ravenous horrors upon the planet.</p> <p>I’m Noah Clark, a streamer famous for my ability to beat co-op games while playing solo. The System doesn’t care if we live or die, but I was able to pick the hidden summoner class, so I’ve got access to game breaking mechanics that just might give me a chance.</p> <p>The System is uncompromising and built to kill, but I will defy it.</p>"; 
